  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study investigates the effects of home-based resistance exercise training, compared to a
      control group, on body composition, muscle strength and glycaemic control in people with type
      2 diabetes.

      Half participants will be in the home-based exercise group and half in the control group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
